    • Method Detail

      • importInstitutions

        public void importInstitutions(java.lang.String institutionsCsv)
        Function to import instititions from an CSV file. For every line in the file, except a header line, an instace of Web:Institution will be created. Institution URL will be used as an unique node key. The nodes with the same key will NOT be overwritten.
        Parameters:
        institutionsCsv - A path to institutions.csv file
